      <t:profileDesc xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">
         <t:abstract><t:p>The general record for the Vita of Gabra Manfas Qǝddus, may be transmitted as part of the <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1119DossierQMQ">hagiographic collection of texts</t:ref> which also includes <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3977Taammer">Miracles</t:ref> and <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2915RepCh196">Hymns</t:ref> in honour of St Gabra Manfas Qǝddus. It may be transmitted in several recensions, <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4074GadlaMA">Gadla Gabra Manfas
                                                  Qǝddus A</t:ref>, <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4075GadlaMB">Gadla Gabra Manfas
                                                  Qǝddus B</t:ref>, and <t:ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4076GadlaMC">Gadla Gabra Manfas
                                                  Qǝddus C</t:ref>.</t:p></t:abstract> 
